{
  "chapter": 56,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十六回 作法自毙。慕容姐妹与小仙女联手围攻一名黑衣蒙面人，黑衣人武功高强，以进为退后擒住慕容珊珊作为人质，双方僵持不下。南宫柳、秦剑与顾人玉赶到，告知众人九妹并不在江别鹤居所，众人开始怀疑是否被栽赃。黑衣人趁机将矛头转向暗处藏匿的小鱼儿。关键时刻慕容九妹突然出现，初时精神恍惚不认得姐妹，听到\"小鱼儿\"之名后恢复记忆，揭露江别鹤曾用迷药控制她并逼婚。众人再度围攻黑衣人，黑衣人忽然揭开蒙面巾——满面虬髯，并非江别鹤本人。他大喝\"江别鹤就在这里\"，冲入小鱼儿藏身之处，剧情急转直下，留下巨大悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "三妹，现在你说怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先拿下他再说吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "text": "你们还要不要她的命？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "快放手，否则我就宰了你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "text": "你们若不放手，我就宰了她！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你先放，我们就放。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "男儿不该与女子争先，还是你们先放吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "我们怎能信得过你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "text": "我也未见能信得过你们！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "text": "二姐你们切切不可放手，他是决计不敢伤我的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我素来沉得住气，就这样耗下去也没关系。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你究竟要这样耗到几时？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "直到你们放手为止。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "呆子，你还不过来帮忙？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢过来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_jian",
      "speaker_name": "秦剑",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "这……这究竟是怎么回事，朋友有话好说。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事纯属误会，但事已至此，我纵然解释，你们也是不会相信的，什么话只有等我先走出去再说了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_liu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫柳",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "阁下莫非真的是江大侠？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么狗屁的大侠，此人正是江别鹤！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们先别管我，先问问九妹可曾找着了么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_liu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫柳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我等方才已到江大侠的居所去了一次……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九妹难道不在那里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_jian",
      "speaker_name": "秦剑",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "你先别管九妹，你自己……你自己……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_liu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫柳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九妹并不在江大侠那里，我等只怕是全都被人捉弄了！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_jian",
      "speaker_name": "秦剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我等方才也见过了那花无缺公子和铁心兰姑娘，都说九妹早已失踪，绝不会和江大侠有关。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁心兰想来是不至于帮江别鹤说话的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也早已觉得此事有些不对，试想江大侠若存心要我们赎金，为何要自己出头？纵然他自己来了，又怎会不知道我们是谁？何况，他要将九妹藏起，地方也多得是，又何必藏在自己的居处？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_jian",
      "speaker_name": "秦剑",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "这件事你既然早已想到，为何还要与江大侠动手？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……江大侠自己一句话不说，咱们怎会知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "但……阁下是否真的是江别鹤大侠？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "误会既已解开，在下是否江别鹤都是一样的了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "贱妾等伤了江大侠那么多属下，实是罪该万死，但望江大侠恕罪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "双方既已出手，伤亡自所难免，又怎能怪得了夫人，只是，那暗中陷害我等的人，却实在可恨！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，那人的确是不能放过！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若找着了那人，先割下他的舌头，挖出他的眼睛，再问问他为什么要使出这害死人的毒计。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "到了这时，阁下还不出来么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你既然早已知道他藏在这里，为何不早说？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "text": "那时我见到暗器自这里飞出，击伤了在下的同伴，还以为是夫人们预先将人埋伏在这里的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友再不自己出来，在下便要令人发箭了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且叫你见识见识慕容姑娘弓箭上的本领！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里好热闹呀，莫非是看戏么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "text": "你们是谁？我不认得你们呀！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "九妹……你……你难道连二姐都不认得了么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "九妹，你怎地会变得如此模样？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "九妹！你认得我么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "她连二姐三姐都不认得了，又怎会认得你？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁将她害成这样子？是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她见了小鱼儿死而复活，所以才吓成这样子的。其实小鱼儿根本没有死，是故意吓吓她的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "谁是小鱼儿？他现在哪里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "text": "现在只怕是死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "你方才说他未死，此刻又说他死，他到底死了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他本来没有死，后来却跌下悬崖死了。但这人一肚子鬼主意，一身鬼本事，别人明明算定他死了，他却常常没有死，没有亲眼瞧见他的尸身，谁也不敢说他是否真的死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他还没有死。我最近又瞧过他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你知道他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "依我看来，他此刻只怕就在……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小鱼儿……小鱼儿！我想起来了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你……你什么都想起来了么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "text": "你是二姐。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "九妹……九妹……天可怜见，你终于好了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "text": "三姐……三姐，我还能见着你们？我这是在做梦么？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那江小鱼将令妹害成如此模样，江湖中谁也放不过他的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若知道那小贼在哪里，不宰了他才怪。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这事其实是怪不得小鱼儿的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "不怪他怪谁？你岂非恨他入骨的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xian_nv",
      "text": "我见他死而复活，当时骇了一跳，虽然有些迷迷糊糊，但过了没有多久，便已渐渐清醒了过来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你既然早已清醒，为何方才不认得我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是被江别鹤害的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他见我清醒，就又以迷药迷住了我，他想乘我晕迷时，逼我和他……和他成亲，为的也是想做慕容家的女婿，他日日夜夜看着我，直到方才，我见他不在，才偷偷溜出来的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个可恶的江别鹤，咱们竟险些被他骗过了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_liu",
      "speaker_name": "南宫柳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪我等方才寻不着她，原来她已自己逃出。幸亏老天有眼，叫她逃来这里，这当真是天网恢恢，疏而不漏。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "江别鹤，你到现在还有何话说？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我是江别鹤？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "慕容双",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_shan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "慕容珊珊",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你若不是江别鹤，江别鹤在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤就在这里！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    }
